sequenceDiagram
    participant T as Terminal
    participant F as Framework
    participant M as Menu Bar
    participant A as Application
    participant D as Dialog

    T->>F: F5 keypress
    F->>M: Keyboard event
    M->>M: Match F5 to command
    M->>F: Generate CMD_SET_BIRTH_DATE
    F->>A: Command event
    A->>A: Match command
    A->>D: Show dialog
    D->>A: Return with date
    A->>A: Update command state
    A->>F: Idle broadcast
    F->>M: CM_COMMAND_SET_CHANGED
    M->>M: Update display
